{
  "texts": [
    "Image Standardization: To produce a uniform input format for the deep learning models, images are standardized in terms of size, color depth, and orientation. 2.",
    "Noise Reduction: Methods for reducing noise are used to enhance image quality and eliminate artifacts that could obstruct analysis. 3.",
    "Anonymization and Privacy Protection: To safeguard privacy and adhere to medical rules, patient data is anonymized. 4.",
    "Data Augmentation: Techniques like rotation, flipping, and contrast adjustment are used to artificially expand the dataset's diversity in order to address difficulties with data shortage.",
    "Design of Deep Learning Models Deep learning techniques are used by Vision Saver to accomplish its objectives."
  ]
}